  ('dietitian-moex-07190', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '某營養師應聘到某國中擔任營養師，設計午餐應採取下列那個基準？', '["熱量650大卡、蛋白質20～23公克、脂肪22公克", "熱量750大卡、蛋白質23～26公克、脂肪26公克", "熱量850大卡、蛋白質25～30公克、脂肪28公克", "熱量950大卡、蛋白質28～33公克、脂肪32公克"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d0d9dce1f2b6", "answer_pdf_sha1": "4729c852d3de", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102110", "c": "106", "s": "0305", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第二次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體技術人員、法醫師語言聽力牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-07191', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者不屬於健康促進學校的主要工作？', '["提升學校供餐品質", "促進學生心理健康", "增進學生學業成就", "加強社區關係"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d0d9dce1f2b6", "answer_pdf_sha1": "4729c852d3de", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102110", "c": "106", "s": "0305", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第二次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體技術人員、法醫師語言聽力牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
